name: Annandale
description: Annandale is a master-planned community offering single-family homes with onsite amenities, now selling in the peaceful suburbia of Garner, NC.

amenities.name: Swimming Pool
amenities.description: Make a splash at the private swimming pool, featuring lap lanes, a slide and a kid-friendly splash area

amenities.name: Clubhouse
amenities.description: The clubhouse includes an elegant main gathering area with a fireplace and communal kitchen to host events

amenities.name: Fitness Center
amenities.description: Stay active, work on endurance and feel the burn at the fully equipped fitness center

amenities.name: Playground
amenities.description: Kids can enjoy hours of outdoor fun at the colorful playground, equipped with slides and a climbing wall

homesites.name: 211 Tennyson Dr
homesites.overview: This new two-story home has ample space for the whole family. The first floor has an open layout among the family room, breakfast nook and kitchen, while a formal dining room by the entrance and a back patio offer additional hosting options. On the same level is a versatile bedroom ideal for overnight visitors. Upstairs are a game room and four bedrooms, including the owner’s suite with a spa-style bathroom.

This expansive two-story home features a flex room and formal dining room bordering the foyer, followed by an open-concept main living area to promote simplified everyday living. Along with a first-floor bedroom ideal for overnight guests. Upstairs is sprawling owner’s suite with a spa-style bathroom, two secondary bedrooms and a spacious game room.

This new two-story home is a family haven in all seasons. The main level has an open space among the family room, a kitchen, a dining room, along with a private study and a bedroom ideal for guests. An attached patio is perfect for morning coffee and evening meals. All the upstairs bedrooms have walk-in closets, while a loft adds versatility.

Exuding sophistication and luxury, this expansive home presents two stories of gracious living space. On the first floor is an inviting family room, chef-ready kitchen and a breakfast nook with direct access to a patio. It’s framed by a practical study, formal dining room and a versatile bedroom well-suited for overnight guests. Upstairs is a sprawling owner’s suite, three secondary bedrooms and a spacious game room to entertain gatherings.

Along with a first-floor bedroom ideal for overnight guests. Upstairs is sprawling owner’s suite with a spa-style bathroom, two secondary bedrooms and a spacious game room.

This two-story home is the largest plan in the collection. Off the foyer is a spacious flex room and formal dining room, followed by an open main living area and a patio for outdoor living. Ideal for overnight guests is a first-floor bedroom. Upstairs is the luxurious owner’s suite, three secondary bedrooms and a generous game room with endless possibilities.
